Package: linux-headers-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-raspi 
Description: Raspberry Pi Linux kernel headers
 This package will always depend on the latest Raspberry Pi Linux
 kernel headers available.

Package: linux-image-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-${kernel-abi-version}-raspi, linux-firmware
Description: Raspberry Pi Linux kernel image
 This package will always depend on the latest Raspberry Pi Linux
 kernel image available.

Package: linux-tools-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-tools-${kernel-abi-version}-raspi
Description: Raspberry Pi Linux kernel tools
 This package will always depend on the latest Raspberry Pi Linux
 kernel tools available.

Package: linux-raspi${variant:suffix}
Architecture: armhf arm64
Section: kernel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-raspi${variant:suffix} (= ${binary:Version}), linux-headers-raspi${variant:suffix} (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Raspberry Pi Linux kernel and headers
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Raspberry Pi Linux
 kernel and headers available.
